              "content": "<p> See 2:248; 4:163; 6:84; 7:122, 142; 10:75; 19:28; 19:53; 20:30, 70, 90-94; 21:48; 23:45-46; 25:35-36; 26:13, 48; 28:34-35; 37:114-122. </p>",
              "sectionId": "book-eighteen-god-s-messenger-aaron-harun-the-distinctive-station-of-his-descendents-in-the-mosaic-dispensation"
